thread.title_full: Frames Direct reviewed by Jay B

author: Jay B
title: Jay B
text: I had been searching for a replacement for my favorite sunglasses, and came across these Wiley X XL-1 Advanced. After looking for deals, I came across FramesDirect, and found they had the best price, especially with their coupon code. And with the free shipping, that sealed the deal. So far I'm very happy with my purchase.
